WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 10=

01:53.580 --> 01:55.140
When you raided the enemy camp

01:55.420 --> 01:56.700
and dueled with Fifteen,

01:57.270 --> 01:58.780
you were like an unfeeling spirit.

01:59.780 --> 02:01.580
But now, you whine like a spoiled baby.

02:24.020 --> 02:24.860
Simu.

02:35.510 --> 02:36.350
What did you call me?

02:38.550 --> 02:39.460
Your Grace,

02:42.740 --> 02:44.070
can I call you Simu?

02:45.620 --> 02:47.140
It makes me feel closer to you.

02:55.550 --> 02:57.070
I'm nearly 400 years older than you.

02:58.140 --> 02:59.790
Choose your words carefully.

03:01.230 --> 03:02.230
I like it.

03:18.420 --> 03:19.300
Like what?

03:21.230 --> 03:22.350
Your name.

03:25.350 --> 03:26.270
I'll make a wish now.

03:28.140 --> 03:29.180
Every time we make a deal,

03:30.740 --> 03:31.950
please allow me

03:35.020 --> 03:35.860
to call you Simu.

03:46.180 --> 03:47.270
You could have asked me

03:47.270 --> 03:48.300
for a lot more things.

03:49.350 --> 03:51.020
They'll help you achieve your wishes.

03:52.180 --> 03:53.790
You shouldn't have wasted the chance.

03:54.550 --> 03:55.700
This is my wish.

03:58.070 --> 03:58.950
To get to know you.

04:02.670 --> 04:03.860
To get to know He Simu.

04:07.020 --> 04:08.390
Now, borrow my sense of touch.

04:11.180 --> 04:12.020
You'll feel happy

04:12.700 --> 04:13.580
and I'll feel well.

04:14.950 --> 04:15.790
Do it.

04:20.910 --> 04:21.750
Young general,

04:23.260 --> 04:24.590
don't bother trying to know me.

04:26.590 --> 04:27.740
You just need to stay alive

04:28.910 --> 04:30.110
and make deals with me.

04:32.540 --> 04:37.870
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

04:38.200 --> 04:42.450
♪Light encountered shadow♪

04:43.810 --> 04:49.180
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

04:49.480 --> 04:54.080
♪The unbreakable fate♪

04:55.170 --> 04:57.010
♪Suddenly cracked♪

04:59.670 --> 05:02.830
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

05:02.830 --> 05:05.360
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

05:05.360 --> 05:10.880
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

05:10.880 --> 05:14.120
♪Following fate's guidance♪

05:14.120 --> 05:18.980
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

05:19.320 --> 05:22.340
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

07:02.590 --> 07:03.430
Skin.

07:13.790 --> 07:14.630
Breath.

07:21.550 --> 07:22.590
Lip.

07:29.620 --> 07:30.460
Pulse.

07:41.670 --> 07:42.510
Heartbeat.

07:58.500 --> 07:59.340
Bite me.

08:00.260 --> 08:01.100
Bite you?

08:03.030 --> 08:03.870
Bite me now.

08:33.190 --> 08:34.780
It hurts.

08:50.260 --> 08:51.100
Simu,

08:52.500 --> 08:54.310
welcome to the Mortal World.

09:01.020 --> 09:02.860
So this is what it feels like to live.

09:07.260 --> 09:08.100
Simu,

09:10.380 --> 09:11.230
have you ever

09:11.230 --> 09:12.230
really lived?

09:38.990 --> 09:39.860
My spirit power.

09:41.710 --> 09:43.230
When you have my senses,

09:45.190 --> 09:46.380
your power is gone?

09:59.260 --> 10:00.900
The sense swap only lasts ten days.

10:01.540 --> 10:02.710
If you dare do anything to me,

10:03.260 --> 10:04.540
you'll be dead in ten days.

10:05.590 --> 10:06.430
Ten days?

10:07.740 --> 10:09.110
Then I'll only live for ten days.

10:10.190 --> 10:11.030
What do you think?

10:11.830 --> 10:12.710
What are you doing?

10:21.740 --> 10:22.740
What feeling is this?

10:25.350 --> 10:26.190
It's itching.

10:27.110 --> 10:27.950
Itching?

10:29.540 --> 10:30.500
I'll tell you a secret.

10:30.990 --> 10:32.190
I'm extremely sensitive.

10:32.660 --> 10:33.590
So, I'm very ticklish.

10:34.020 --> 10:34.950
Every time you leaned

10:34.950 --> 10:36.020
or you touched me,

10:36.620 --> 10:37.620
I struggled to hold back.

10:42.350 --> 10:43.470
I'll make you suffer

10:44.590 --> 10:45.500
just as I did.

10:52.020 --> 10:53.500
You're going to die in ten days.

10:53.780 --> 10:55.100
Then I'll make the days worth.

10:55.780 --> 10:57.230
Wa... Wait. Stop!

10:57.350 --> 10:58.190
Stop that!

11:10.380 --> 11:11.230
It doesn't hurt.

11:15.780 --> 11:16.620
It really doesn't.

11:17.540 --> 11:19.260
It was the same when I touched you.

11:22.430 --> 11:23.500
So this is what the world

11:27.540 --> 11:29.260
has always felt like to you.

11:38.470 --> 11:39.350
Why do you want

11:40.740 --> 11:41.780
to get to know me?

11:42.230 --> 11:43.070
Like why you tried

11:43.070 --> 11:43.990
to get to know me.

11:44.590 --> 11:45.430
You're special.

11:47.070 --> 11:47.910
You make me curious.

11:54.590 --> 11:56.190
You're just a fragile mortal.

11:57.310 --> 11:58.310
Too much curiosity

11:59.310 --> 12:00.150
will get you killed.

12:05.140 --> 12:05.980
I'm not afraid.

12:19.780 --> 12:20.620
How did it

12:20.620 --> 12:21.620
get this messy overnight?

12:22.070 --> 12:22.950
I don't know.

12:22.950 --> 12:24.740
Even the dirt and grass are torn up.

12:24.950 --> 12:26.590
Come on, everybody. Let's clean it up.

12:26.590 --> 12:27.540
- Why?
- Look.

12:27.540 --> 12:28.670
Help me set this upright.

12:28.670 --> 12:29.540
Let's tidy it up.

12:29.540 --> 12:30.380
Come on.

12:30.860 --> 12:31.950
What happened here?

12:31.950 --> 12:33.380
No idea. Let's just clean. Come on.

12:33.380 --> 12:34.220
How did this happen?

12:34.740 --> 12:35.990
Let's move this over there.

12:36.140 --> 12:36.980
What about this?

12:43.020 --> 12:44.140
Oh, I almost forgot.

12:47.070 --> 12:48.350
I have no sense of touch now.

14:04.710 --> 14:05.590
Sweep over there.

14:05.590 --> 14:06.480
General,

14:06.540 --> 14:07.470
is the door bolt broken?

14:07.740 --> 14:08.760
I'll have it repaired.

14:08.760 --> 14:09.620
Clean up the soil

14:09.620 --> 14:10.460
and the grass.

14:10.590 --> 14:11.430
Thank you.

14:11.740 --> 14:12.520
The rooms are cleaned.

14:12.520 --> 14:13.400
What’s going on here?

14:13.830 --> 14:15.020
This is really strange.

14:16.390 --> 14:17.280
You, come over.

14:18.270 --> 14:19.370
Move it over there.

14:19.380 --> 14:21.070
Sorry to have woken you up, General.

14:21.830 --> 14:23.380
No one knows what happened last night.

14:23.500 --> 14:24.340
This morning,

14:24.500 --> 14:25.620
it looks like thieves came.

14:26.020 --> 14:27.590
(Fucui Chamber)
It's a mess everywhere.

14:27.900 --> 14:29.260
A lot of things are damaged.

14:29.710 --> 14:31.660
Looks like they were crushed.

14:32.020 --> 14:33.140
Even groceries in the kitchen

14:33.140 --> 14:33.990
were messed up.

14:34.070 --> 14:34.950
Our chickens and ducks

14:35.140 --> 14:36.140
got completely plucked.

14:37.260 --> 14:38.110
Was anything stolen?

14:38.500 --> 14:39.620
Nothing was stolen.

14:40.470 --> 14:41.470
It's more like rats

14:41.620 --> 14:42.710
than thieves.

14:43.110 --> 14:44.430
But the rats

14:44.860 --> 14:45.990
were pretty savage.

14:47.830 --> 14:48.670
All right.

14:48.860 --> 14:49.710
Oh, General.

14:49.740 --> 14:50.860
Be careful, General.

14:53.070 --> 14:54.110
Two more, come here.

14:54.360 --> 14:55.230
Coming.

14:55.350 --> 14:56.190
Yes.

15:00.080 --> 15:01.240
- All right.
- All right.

15:30.620 --> 15:31.460
Simu.

15:34.020 --> 15:34.860
Look.

15:38.350 --> 15:40.110
Your Grace, did you stay up all night

15:40.430 --> 15:41.500
experiencing this sense?

15:43.260 --> 15:44.900
I was just looking around casually.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.620
Suddenly, it was morning.

15:47.020 --> 15:48.260
No wonder mortals always say,

15:48.260 --> 15:49.860
"Time slips away so fast."

15:51.020 --> 15:52.110
For mortals like you,

15:52.780 --> 15:54.020
time is really a bit short.

15:54.900 --> 15:55.740
It seems

15:56.380 --> 15:57.660
you had a wonderful night.

16:05.310 --> 16:06.150
Come on.

16:20.620 --> 16:21.460
Wipe it.

16:24.110 --> 16:25.620
I can't control my strength now.

16:26.860 --> 16:27.700
You wipe it yourself.

16:29.900 --> 16:30.740
Not here.

16:31.070 --> 16:32.310
The left cheek.

16:44.310 --> 16:45.150
And your forehead.

16:51.830 --> 16:52.740
I guess you've explored

16:52.740 --> 16:53.580
the entire residence.

16:54.380 --> 16:55.990
Shall I take you to the market?

16:56.540 --> 16:57.620
I can go myself.

16:57.950 --> 16:58.860
You don't need to go.

17:01.190 --> 17:02.860
I don't want to hear more stories

17:03.780 --> 17:04.670
about rampaging rats.

17:05.340 --> 17:06.180
What did you say?

17:06.820 --> 17:08.500
(Ginger honey water,
Perilla tea, River water tea)

17:09.230 --> 17:10.260
Ginger honey water.

17:10.500 --> 17:12.190
Tasty ginger honey water.

17:12.390 --> 17:13.820
Miss, would you like some?

17:14.430 --> 17:15.670
Be careful, it's hot.

17:16.150 --> 17:17.100
Are you all right?

17:20.100 --> 17:21.710
Come take a look.

17:21.710 --> 17:23.300
Big and sweet fruit.

17:23.300 --> 17:24.500
Miss, look at the apples.

17:25.300 --> 17:26.740
These are tangerines. Very sweet.

17:28.780 --> 17:30.580
Miss, they're sweet. Buy some.

17:32.430 --> 17:33.740
Chestnuts.

17:34.150 --> 17:34.990
Chestnuts.

17:35.500 --> 17:37.020
Miss, two wen each.

17:37.020 --> 17:38.460
- Buy some.
- They're sweet.

17:38.580 --> 17:39.420
Very tasty.

17:41.260 --> 17:42.340
Miss, don't do this.

17:42.500 --> 17:43.670
Unless you're buying.

17:43.670 --> 17:45.180
Hey, Miss. Please don't.

17:45.300 --> 17:46.150
No, Miss.

17:47.110 --> 17:47.950
He'll pay.

17:47.950 --> 17:49.310
I'll have to take them home.

17:49.430 --> 17:50.630
My chestnuts are very sweet.

17:51.150 --> 17:51.990
Would you like some?

17:54.500 --> 17:55.340
Are you all right?

17:55.820 --> 17:56.820
Would you like some?

17:57.100 --> 17:57.940
Be careful.

17:58.100 --> 17:59.390
Freshly baked flatbread.

17:59.580 --> 18:00.740
Excuse me. Make way, please.

18:00.770 --> 18:01.640
Watch out.

18:01.710 --> 18:02.550
Flatbread.

18:02.790 --> 18:03.630
Come take a look.

18:04.430 --> 18:06.820
Is this young man drunk?

18:07.390 --> 18:08.870
What... What is wrong with him?

18:08.870 --> 18:09.710
Sorry.

18:10.150 --> 18:10.990
Sorry.

18:11.020 --> 18:12.260
- Take a look.
- Chestnuts.

18:12.260 --> 18:13.100
It's nicely made.

18:13.390 --> 18:14.870
Come try some chestnuts.

18:15.190 --> 18:16.820
You can try on these jewels.

18:16.820 --> 18:17.660
Take a look.

18:19.060 --> 18:20.100
Sorry, sir.

18:20.430 --> 18:21.300
Sorry.

18:21.300 --> 18:22.140
I'm sorry.

18:27.100 --> 18:28.100
Why are you crying?

18:37.580 --> 18:38.500
With no sense of touch,

18:38.710 --> 18:40.390
you can't feel your own body.

18:41.390 --> 18:42.340
So, your sense of space

18:42.340 --> 18:43.300
gets thrown off.

18:43.870 --> 18:44.710
At this time,

18:47.870 --> 18:49.230
you must learn

18:49.430 --> 18:50.780
to use your sight

18:51.390 --> 18:53.150
to judge the distance

18:53.820 --> 18:54.710
between your body...

18:56.150 --> 18:57.670
And other objects.

19:01.630 --> 19:02.630
Miss, you...

19:02.630 --> 19:03.470
He'll pay.

19:06.020 --> 19:07.710
Sir, these jewels...

19:08.950 --> 19:10.190
They haven't been paid.

19:10.190 --> 19:11.300
You need to pay.

19:12.670 --> 19:13.870
Miss, it's...

19:14.020 --> 19:15.020
It's for squeezing.

19:15.150 --> 19:16.910
Look, you've ruined them.

19:19.780 --> 19:20.950
You just love squeezing, huh?

19:22.020 --> 19:22.860
Foxy,

19:23.060 --> 19:23.910
come and pay.

19:25.780 --> 19:26.620
Fine.

19:26.880 --> 19:27.730
You've squeezed them,

19:27.740 --> 19:28.580
and you'll pay.

19:29.020 --> 19:30.670
Sir, you have to pay for all these.

19:32.150 --> 19:32.990
Miss,

19:33.150 --> 19:33.990
pinwheels for sale.

19:36.540 --> 19:37.380
Here I am!

19:47.150 --> 19:48.300
Look, she squeezed them all.

19:48.820 --> 19:49.660
Sir.

19:49.870 --> 19:50.720
How much?

19:50.740 --> 19:51.600
Ten wen.

19:51.610 --> 19:52.520
Fine.

19:52.740 --> 19:53.630
Hey, gentleman.

19:53.670 --> 19:54.950
You haven't paid me yet.

19:55.260 --> 19:56.430
And me.

19:56.430 --> 19:57.430
Look, it's crushed.

19:57.820 --> 19:59.430
You owe me fifteen wen, too.

19:59.580 --> 20:01.020
And you owe me thirty-five.

20:01.150 --> 20:02.150
She crushed everything.

20:02.340 --> 20:03.710
- Yeah.
- You have to pay for all.

20:03.950 --> 20:04.950
- That's right.
- Yeah.

20:04.950 --> 20:06.110
- I'll pay.
- Exactly.

20:06.230 --> 20:07.190
That's right.

20:28.430 --> 20:29.270
(Is this world)

20:31.500 --> 20:32.670
(really this lovely?)

20:33.670 --> 20:39.330
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

20:40.040 --> 20:45.790
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

20:46.200 --> 20:52.270
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

20:53.390 --> 20:57.650
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

20:58.440 --> 21:01.190
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

21:01.190 --> 21:02.730
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

21:03.340 --> 21:04.710
They say fingers speak the heart.

21:06.130 --> 21:07.570
♪I care for no one but you♪

21:07.570 --> 21:09.180
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

21:09.180 --> 21:12.410
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

21:12.780 --> 21:14.390
So am I holding your heart?

21:15.570 --> 21:18.360
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

21:18.540 --> 21:21.020
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

21:21.020 --> 21:24.920
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

21:44.700 --> 21:50.060
(Shuozhou)

22:06.950 --> 22:07.790
Marshal Qin,

22:08.340 --> 22:09.430
we await your presence!

22:10.230 --> 22:12.390
We await your presence, Marshal!

22:13.220 --> 22:15.660
(Qin Huanda, Marshal of Great Liang)

22:17.190 --> 22:18.470
I'm Fang Xianye,
the Censorial Counselor.

22:18.820 --> 22:19.710
Welcome, Marshal.

22:20.540 --> 22:21.380
Counselor,

22:21.670 --> 22:22.510
no need for that.

22:23.340 --> 22:24.430
You've just taken over

22:24.430 --> 22:25.390
the city affairs.

22:25.630 --> 22:26.500
How's it going?

22:26.950 --> 22:28.470
Things are messy and yet to be sorted.

22:29.060 --> 22:29.900
But the citizens

22:30.020 --> 22:31.060
cooperate with the reforms.

22:31.500 --> 22:32.340
So far, so good.

22:32.780 --> 22:33.620
Glad to hear that.

22:33.870 --> 22:35.260
I'm counting on you

22:35.430 --> 22:36.390
to handle this.

22:37.910 --> 22:39.020
Thank you for asking.

22:41.150 --> 22:43.190
Why isn't Duan Xu here?

22:44.500 --> 22:45.780
General Duan is severely injured.

22:45.950 --> 22:47.190
So, he can't come to greet you.

22:47.710 --> 22:48.580
Please forgive him.

22:49.100 --> 22:49.940
What?

22:52.390 --> 22:53.430
He has arranged

22:53.430 --> 22:55.260
a welcome feast for all of you.

22:56.020 --> 22:57.710
Everybody, please come.

23:07.940 --> 23:13.180
(Shuozhou Yamen)

23:20.190 --> 23:21.060
I'm Duan Xu of Tabai.

23:21.430 --> 23:22.270
Greetings, Marshal.

23:23.630 --> 23:24.470
Greetings, Generals.

23:35.670 --> 23:36.910
I'm severely injured,

23:37.390 --> 23:38.230
so I didn't meet you.

23:39.300 --> 23:40.340
Please forgive me.

23:41.020 --> 23:42.670
Marshal Qin had a long trip.

23:43.710 --> 23:45.100
And this is where you settle him?

23:45.670 --> 23:47.300
The battle in Shuozhou has just ended.

23:48.340 --> 23:49.540
The Yamen

23:50.390 --> 23:51.580
is actually the tidiest place.

23:52.990 --> 23:53.950
I believe

23:55.020 --> 23:56.190
Marshal Qin wouldn't mind.

23:57.500 --> 23:58.430
General Duan,

23:58.950 --> 24:00.630
you're truly a young talent.

24:00.990 --> 24:02.580
In Shuozhou, you confronted

24:02.580 --> 24:04.390
200,000 Chong soldiers
for over two months.

24:04.740 --> 24:05.670
Then, you sneaked in

24:05.670 --> 24:06.670
and killed Awo'erqi

24:06.670 --> 24:07.670
to turn the tide.

24:07.990 --> 24:08.870
I've reported

24:09.230 --> 24:10.630
your achievements.

24:11.100 --> 24:12.340
You'll surely be rewarded soon.

24:13.710 --> 24:14.870
Thank you for entrusting me

24:14.870 --> 24:15.820
with that mission.

24:16.630 --> 24:17.470
I didn't fall short.

24:18.740 --> 24:20.430
Now, the Chong court is in chaos.

24:20.780 --> 24:21.670
It's the perfect time

24:21.670 --> 24:22.740
when we can save the people

24:22.740 --> 24:23.580
in the north.

24:24.470 --> 24:25.820
We must press our advantage

24:25.820 --> 24:26.660
and keep going north.

24:28.060 --> 24:29.300
As for the target city...

24:31.230 --> 24:32.100
Generals,

24:33.020 --> 24:34.150
what are your opinions?

24:34.870 --> 24:36.230
Youzhou, to the northeast,

24:36.540 --> 24:37.540
is in a key location.

24:37.780 --> 24:39.300
It's a strategic battleground.

24:40.470 --> 24:41.390
I second that.

24:42.500 --> 24:43.580
If we don't seize Youzhou

24:43.580 --> 24:45.340
while our enemy is in chaos,

24:45.990 --> 24:47.300
we may never get another chance.

24:47.910 --> 24:50.710
Youzhou has offensive
and defensive advantages.

24:51.100 --> 24:52.390
Once we occupy it,

24:52.820 --> 24:53.950
Chong will never retake it.

24:54.540 --> 24:55.380
General Duan,

24:55.670 --> 24:56.710
any objections?

24:57.340 --> 24:58.910
Youzhou is strategically vital.

24:59.470 --> 25:00.580
However chaotic the Chong factions are,

25:00.990 --> 25:02.340
they will unite against us,

25:02.630 --> 25:03.910
regardless of their grudges.

25:04.780 --> 25:05.630
So, in my opinion,

25:06.670 --> 25:07.950
we should target

25:07.950 --> 25:08.790
Yunzhou and Luozhou.

25:14.990 --> 25:16.190
When I just walked in,

25:16.780 --> 25:17.740
I noticed you were

25:18.060 --> 25:19.870
quite interested in my armor.

25:20.910 --> 25:21.750
Even my brother

25:22.580 --> 25:23.540
who is 10 years old

25:23.540 --> 25:24.380
can lift this armor.

25:25.020 --> 25:25.860
But it's unbreakable

25:26.150 --> 25:26.990
and impenetrable.

25:41.060 --> 25:42.430
This armor is light and sturdy.

25:43.150 --> 25:44.100
Very formidable, indeed.

25:46.870 --> 25:48.020
This kind of armor

25:48.910 --> 25:50.260
is forged from Tianluo Ore.

25:50.870 --> 25:51.820
Very rare in our state.

25:52.630 --> 25:53.820
It's abundant in Luozhou,

25:54.740 --> 25:55.990
the city named after it.

25:56.950 --> 25:57.810
Chong captured Luozhou

25:57.820 --> 25:59.060
and ignorantly massacred its people.

25:59.570 --> 26:00.430
Now they know nothing

26:00.430 --> 26:01.320
about how to refine

26:01.320 --> 26:02.290
this kind of ore.

26:02.670 --> 26:03.510
As for Yunzhou,

26:03.950 --> 26:05.150
it can be used for warhorses.

26:05.820 --> 26:07.260
That would narrow the gap

26:07.580 --> 26:08.420
between two armies.

26:11.820 --> 26:13.150
The grasslands of Yunzhou

26:13.710 --> 26:14.780
and ore veins of Luozhou

26:15.430 --> 26:16.870
are indeed vital resources.

26:17.670 --> 26:18.990
But the tides of battle

26:18.990 --> 26:19.870
are ever-changing.

26:20.060 --> 26:20.900
One battle

26:21.260 --> 26:22.780
can bring years of peace.

26:23.910 --> 26:25.470
So they believe

26:26.150 --> 26:27.670
Youzhou is the best choice.

26:27.910 --> 26:28.820
But Marshal...

26:30.150 --> 26:30.990
General Duan,

26:31.260 --> 26:32.190
I've heard

26:32.190 --> 26:33.910
about an extraordinary lady in your army

26:34.340 --> 26:36.260
who can read the stars
to predict the weather.

26:36.950 --> 26:38.020
Youzhou happens to be

26:38.190 --> 26:39.740
a place with changeable weather.

26:40.230 --> 26:41.820
So, would you be willing

26:42.230 --> 26:44.710
to lend this lady to me?

26:45.710 --> 26:46.550
No.

26:47.020 --> 26:47.950
We face a great crisis.

26:48.950 --> 26:50.580
How could you keep her for yourself?

26:51.390 --> 26:52.230
General Duan,

26:52.910 --> 26:53.870
why don't we hear

26:53.870 --> 26:54.710
what she herself

26:54.710 --> 26:55.670
has to say?

26:56.230 --> 26:57.070
What do you think?

26:59.100 --> 26:59.940
Chenying,

27:00.470 --> 27:01.390
go get her here.

27:02.360 --> 27:03.230
But...

27:03.240 --> 27:04.080
It's all right.

27:06.740 --> 27:07.580
Just go.

27:38.870 --> 27:39.710
Xiaoxiao.

27:40.910 --> 27:42.430
General sent me to invite you.

27:51.300 --> 27:56.340
(Clear-sighted and Astute)

28:02.020 --> 28:02.860
Miss He,

28:04.470 --> 28:05.470
this is Marshal Qin.

28:09.630 --> 28:11.470
I heard General Duan's several victories

28:11.470 --> 28:13.300
were attributed
to your marvelous predictions.

28:13.820 --> 28:14.950
Marshal Qin wants to move you

28:14.950 --> 28:15.910
up to our army.

28:16.230 --> 28:17.070
Would you be willing?

28:18.670 --> 28:19.510
No.

28:21.540 --> 28:23.060
- What?
- Please understand.

28:23.780 --> 28:25.740
Most things go against our wishes.

28:26.430 --> 28:27.630
When trapped in Shuozhou,

28:27.630 --> 28:28.470
we needed backup.

28:28.630 --> 28:30.060
But no one ever came.

28:31.330 --> 28:32.190
In this world,

28:32.190 --> 28:33.300
not every desire

28:33.300 --> 28:34.260
can be fulfilled.

28:35.190 --> 28:36.030
Miss He,

28:36.580 --> 28:37.950
are you blaming me

28:38.230 --> 28:39.540
for not sending reinforcements?

28:41.430 --> 28:42.740
I'm merely lamenting.

28:43.390 --> 28:44.780
In such peril,

28:45.670 --> 28:46.820
we were alone and helpless.

28:47.820 --> 28:48.660
Therefore,

28:48.950 --> 28:49.990
for the sake of merit,

28:50.340 --> 28:51.710
I offer you this promotion.

28:53.340 --> 28:54.260
Thank you, Marshal.

28:55.580 --> 28:56.710
But I've divined

28:57.190 --> 28:58.820
that General Duan is my destined one.

28:59.230 --> 29:00.470
The secrets of fate I uncover

29:00.470 --> 29:01.630
can only serve him.

29:02.060 --> 29:03.230
If they serve another,

29:04.100 --> 29:05.500
the consequences will be dire.

29:06.670 --> 29:07.780
Orders are absolute!

29:08.260 --> 29:09.870
Such nonsense won't be tolerated!

29:11.260 --> 29:12.340
If I refuse,

29:13.500 --> 29:14.710
what could you possibly do?

29:14.910 --> 29:16.190
How dare you!

29:17.670 --> 29:18.510
Duan Xu!

29:37.230 --> 29:38.070
Marshal,

29:38.780 --> 29:40.150
since she refuses,

29:41.500 --> 29:42.340
no one can take away

29:43.060 --> 29:44.430
my lady.

29:54.470 --> 29:55.630
Thank you for understanding.

29:56.470 --> 29:57.820
My army will still

29:58.540 --> 29:59.820
be yours to command.

30:23.340 --> 30:24.180
Marshal,

30:24.340 --> 30:25.870
Duan Xu is deceitful and insolent.

30:26.470 --> 30:27.310
And that woman.

30:27.820 --> 30:28.710
They're two of a kind!

30:29.060 --> 30:31.260
His family has connections to His Majesty.

30:31.740 --> 30:32.670
We may not suppress him

30:33.020 --> 30:34.260
as we wish.

30:35.060 --> 30:36.190
In the Shuozhou campaign,

30:36.470 --> 30:37.820
I meant to use him as bait.

30:38.430 --> 30:39.740
Never expected this bait

30:40.390 --> 30:43.150
to destroy the enemy instead.

30:47.820 --> 30:48.670
Put me down.

30:49.470 --> 30:50.310
No.

30:51.100 --> 30:52.630
I won't repeat myself.

30:53.630 --> 30:54.470
Don't struggle.

30:54.540 --> 30:56.980
(Shuozhou Yamen)

30:56.990 --> 30:57.950
We have eyes everywhere

30:57.950 --> 30:58.870
watching us.

31:01.990 --> 31:03.260
Let's play it to the end.

31:08.260 --> 31:12.620
(Liang)

31:12.950 --> 31:14.430
After getting the sense of touch,

31:15.100 --> 31:16.340
you stayed up all night.

31:17.540 --> 31:19.300
But a human needs to sleep.

31:20.100 --> 31:21.260
Why don't you

31:22.100 --> 31:22.940
get some sleep now?

31:23.820 --> 31:24.670
No wonder I feel

31:24.670 --> 31:25.990
my eyes are glazing over.

31:27.630 --> 31:28.950
You're getting awfully bold.

31:29.990 --> 31:30.830
Are you so confident

31:30.870 --> 31:31.780
that I won't punish you

31:31.780 --> 31:32.780
in ten days?

31:34.430 --> 31:35.270
I wouldn't dare.

31:35.630 --> 31:36.470
Like I said,

31:37.340 --> 31:38.670
we should play it to the end.

31:39.670 --> 31:40.910
Back in your room,

31:41.870 --> 31:43.260
I will put you down.

31:43.260 --> 31:46.230
♪Snow on sunny days♪

31:46.630 --> 31:49.090
♪Countless wayfarers roam the world♪

31:49.090 --> 31:56.360
♪Luckily, I share a fate with you♪

31:58.210 --> 32:01.720
♪I hold a lantern to draw the moon♪

32:01.970 --> 32:06.000
♪Light up the night that haunts you♪

32:06.480 --> 32:10.510
♪I have simple wishes, but I fear♪

32:10.510 --> 32:13.720
♪The world can't hold them♪

32:13.720 --> 32:17.620
(Shuozhou Yamen)

32:17.620 --> 32:21.410
♪See the world I've never seen♪

32:21.930 --> 32:26.040
♪However the years may wind♪

32:26.040 --> 32:33.040
♪I wish I could live in your heart♪

33:02.540 --> 33:03.380
Simu,

33:05.260 --> 33:06.100
have a sweet dream.

33:13.180 --> 33:14.460
(Liang)

33:24.350 --> 33:25.200
Greetings, Marshal.

33:26.500 --> 33:27.910
No need for formalities.

33:28.300 --> 33:29.140
Take a seat.

33:34.500 --> 33:35.470
You visit me so late.

33:36.390 --> 33:37.230
Anything urgent?

33:37.740 --> 33:39.340
Shunzhou horse ranch lost its ledger.

33:39.780 --> 33:40.820
A registrar is missing too.

33:41.430 --> 33:42.390
Duke Pei is furious.

33:42.870 --> 33:43.780
Horse administration?

33:45.260 --> 33:46.100
Wouldn't that mean

33:46.710 --> 33:48.300
Duke Pei could be implicated?

33:49.630 --> 33:50.470
I'm afraid

33:50.710 --> 33:52.230
Chancellor Du's faction is behind this.

33:52.580 --> 33:54.230
The court is still unaware of this.

33:54.670 --> 33:56.340
I'm going to Shunzhou soon

33:56.580 --> 33:58.470
to investigate the ledger case.

33:59.060 --> 34:00.340
When you're here, Marshal,

34:00.710 --> 34:02.100
you'll surely suppress

34:02.100 --> 34:03.910
Duan Xu's influence within the military.

34:04.500 --> 34:05.630
Duke Pei had planned

34:06.020 --> 34:08.660
to delay the war by attacking Youzhou.

34:09.270 --> 34:10.180
As it seems now,

34:10.330 --> 34:11.180
horse administration

34:11.180 --> 34:12.140
must be the priority.

34:13.700 --> 34:14.620
During the day, Duan Xu

34:14.790 --> 34:15.650
showed intent to seize

34:15.650 --> 34:16.540
Yunzhou and Luozhou.

34:16.700 --> 34:17.830
I didn't want to support him.

34:18.350 --> 34:19.190
But now,

34:19.390 --> 34:20.910
I have no choice but to let him go.

34:21.750 --> 34:23.220
Yunzhou has vast grasslands,

34:23.500 --> 34:24.500
so it's great for horses.

34:24.870 --> 34:26.060
If we capture Yunzhou,

34:26.390 --> 34:27.540
it will make up the deficit

34:27.540 --> 34:28.580
in the horse administration

34:28.830 --> 34:29.990
and help Duke Pei out.

34:37.620 --> 34:39.020
I will present this to him.

34:39.350 --> 34:41.220
Whether Duan Xu captures the two cities,

34:41.540 --> 34:42.390
the court's attention

34:42.390 --> 34:43.300
will be diverted

34:43.470 --> 34:45.390
until we solve the horse administration.

34:47.020 --> 34:48.990
Duan Xu uses cunning tactics in battle.

34:49.390 --> 34:50.540
But you're the one

34:50.870 --> 34:52.220
to make battlefield decisions.

34:52.620 --> 34:53.870
If he wins,

34:54.060 --> 34:55.580
you'll be rewarded as well.

34:56.100 --> 34:57.270
But if he dies in battle,

34:57.830 --> 35:00.100
he'll be accused of reckless deployment.

35:38.310 --> 35:39.580
The wind is so warm.

36:08.990 --> 36:09.830
Father.

36:10.220 --> 36:11.060
Mother.

36:14.350 --> 36:15.190
Simu.

36:15.540 --> 36:16.380
Come here.

36:17.180 --> 36:18.020
Come over to us.

36:22.910 --> 36:23.750
Mother.

36:33.620 --> 36:34.460
Mother,

36:34.700 --> 36:35.540
what's so great

36:35.580 --> 36:36.990
about this tune?

36:37.700 --> 36:39.470
I can't pick out the melody at all.

36:40.470 --> 36:41.750
Neither can your father.

36:42.310 --> 36:43.950
He just knows how to play it.

36:46.180 --> 36:47.750
Your father plays music for me

36:48.310 --> 36:49.430
because he loves me.

36:50.430 --> 36:51.270
He knows

36:51.390 --> 36:52.750
I can feel his love.

36:54.180 --> 36:55.390
This is why

36:55.390 --> 36:56.660
mortals love music.

36:57.950 --> 36:59.220
Because there is love in it.

37:01.140 --> 37:01.980
Simu,

37:03.350 --> 37:04.700
mortals in this world

37:05.470 --> 37:07.180
are sensitive and fragile,

37:07.750 --> 37:09.220
yet passionate and vibrant.

37:09.990 --> 37:11.540
Your power is overwhelming.

37:12.060 --> 37:13.500
You must learn to understand them

37:14.140 --> 37:15.790
and be gentle with them.

37:17.020 --> 37:18.310
Because one day,

37:19.660 --> 37:20.910
you'll protect this world

37:22.470 --> 37:24.790
by balancing spirits and mortals

37:25.390 --> 37:26.540
just as your father did.

37:31.910 --> 37:32.990
(Mother's hands)

37:33.660 --> 37:34.500
(are very warm.)

37:35.470 --> 37:37.060
(Father's hands)

37:37.500 --> 37:38.580
(are very soft, though.)

38:03.580 --> 38:04.420
What's wrong?

38:10.950 --> 38:12.540
I feel some wind inside my body.

38:15.700 --> 38:17.430
Is there wind in every living person?

38:19.470 --> 38:20.350
This is breath.

38:22.700 --> 38:23.540
Breath?

38:27.540 --> 38:28.380
Right.

38:29.220 --> 38:30.180
The wind inside the body

38:31.100 --> 38:32.060
is breath.

38:43.950 --> 38:45.350
Just now, my parents were here.

38:48.620 --> 38:49.580
Did you have a dream?

38:52.870 --> 38:53.710
Dream?

38:54.470 --> 38:55.990
Something mortals have?

38:58.990 --> 38:59.870
Why are you here?

39:03.660 --> 39:04.830
You're getting bolder.

39:05.540 --> 39:06.620
What a waste to be a mortal!

39:09.801 --> 39:15.131
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:15.461 --> 39:19.711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:21.071 --> 39:26.441
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

39:26.741 --> 39:31.341
♪The unbreakable fate♪

39:32.431 --> 39:34.271
♪Suddenly cracked♪

39:46.481 --> 39:51.921
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:52.101 --> 39:56.431
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:57.801 --> 40:03.191
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:03.421 --> 40:07.361
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:09.131 --> 40:11.021
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:13.681 --> 40:16.841
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

40:16.841 --> 40:19.371
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

40:19.371 --> 40:24.891
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

40:24.891 --> 40:28.131
♪Following fate's guidance♪

40:28.131 --> 40:32.991
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

40:33.331 --> 40:36.351
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

40:36.351 --> 40:39.171
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

40:39.431 --> 40:41.961
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

40:41.961 --> 40:47.381
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

40:47.551 --> 40:50.621
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

40:50.781 --> 40:55.681
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

40:55.891 --> 40:59.361
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
